# Project Overview

This CLI tool, ignite-cli, is designed to streamline the development environment setup for mobile, backend, and frontend developers.

## Main Components

- Entry point: [bin/dev-cli.sh](mdc:bin/dev-cli.sh)
- Command implementations: [src/commands](mdc:src/commands)
- Utility functions: [src/utils](mdc:src/utils)
- Project templates: [src/templates](mdc:src/templates)

## Developer Workflow

1. The user selects their developer role (mobile, backend, frontend)
2. The user selects a framework based on their role
3. The tool helps with repository cloning, project structure generation, and configuration
